08:03.620 --> 08:05.980
I ran it on one core and one gig of RAM.

08:06.080 --> 08:07.880
No problem whatsoever.

08:07.980 --> 08:10.180
Yeah, but this thing's based on Debian 9.

08:10.280 --> 08:11.360
Snore.

08:11.460 --> 08:12.800
Wah, wah, wah.

08:12.900 --> 08:14.100
