09:37.680 --> 09:42.480
OK, I got to admit, early on, I'm feeling a little concerned.

09:42.480 --> 09:45.020
Are you feeling competitive right now, Cheese?

09:45.120 --> 09:46.380
Nah.

09:46.480 --> 09:49.260
Yeah, OK, all right, OK.

09:49.360 --> 09:50.160
Damn it, Debian.

09:50.260 --> 09:52.220
So what about easy dark mode?

